					<p>For three column layouts at 1024, I try to make the second column end at or very near 760px and put &#8220;secondary&#8221; information in the third column. That way, if the user is on an 800px monitor the site still feels like it naturally fits their browser, in a sense.</p>

<p>I&#8217;ve used either 980 or 970 before, but using 960 makes perfect sense for its divisability (that&#8217;s probably not a word).</p>
