					21&nbsp;&nbsp;
					<strong>Joshua E Cook</strong> ~ 14 September 2006 at 11:49 AM</p>
					<p>I recently designed a flexible-width site that scales from a minimum of 760px to a maximum of 960px, then remains centered for larger browser widths.  It looks great on displays large and small, IMO.</p>
